---
title: Cal Smart Cranberry-Glazed Turkey Meatballs with Sweet Potato Mash and Parmesan Green Beans
description: In this Thanksgiving-inspired dinner, meatballs are tossed in a cranberry glaze and served with chive sweet potato mash and Parmesan-topped tender green beans.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-glacees-aux-canneberges-39e05b8b.jpg
